empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nesdam1981\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f50699db8a690b904215a0256ee6612b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f50699db8a690b904215a0256ee6612b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nesdam1981\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Nesdam1981</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 2, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s a great plugin in its self. But, the extensions are ridiculously overpriced and more or less requires that you are already making a huge profit from your store. Otherwise it\'s just not worth it.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">excellent and detailed explanation</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fritzke\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25424cd543968c4dee34ada995fa003c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25424cd543968c4dee34ada995fa003c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fritzke\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fritzke</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\nfinally the right solution after many hours </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/darckhang\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d531735650c8ca333d963d9c8575344c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d531735650c8ca333d963d9c8575344c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/darckhang\" class=\"reviewer-name\">darckhang</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">great ecommerce plugin</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">You are the best</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tarikajinah\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0d47f0282cccf695e1a44e0695d320d0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0d47f0282cccf695e1a44e0695d320d0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tarikajinah\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tarikajinah</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">You are a dream that came true. Really! Can\'t express how much impress there is to share about your intuitive, resourceful and limitless open-source website and e-sore builder. Love everything about woocommerce and wordpress but can never get enough! Thank you indeed for facilitating entrepreneurship in this ever changing yet exciting post-covid19 Era.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thank you</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yoannprod19\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e3a10fe338eb1beed201a7b6574daa99?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e3a10fe338eb1beed201a7b6574daa99?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yoannprod19\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yoannprod19</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works perfectly with digital products, thank you for your work !</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">change Permalink-custom base</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kingofthepnu\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40552f507de1525b4ec5c97d1e42c30f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40552f507de1525b4ec5c97d1e42c30f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kingofthepnu\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kingofthepnu</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 18, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hello there,\nI read something about Permalink that products\" should not be change otherwise it\'ll face issues. Can I remove \"product\" and change \"Permalink-custom base\" to %post_id% ?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good for small shops, a nightmare for real ecommerce</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cbdoel\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/120ec65b6d1eb8eef8f9224c4264656a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/120ec65b6d1eb8eef8f9224c4264656a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cbdoel\" class=\"reviewer-name\">CBD-Öl <small>(cbdoel)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Woocommerce is a Shop Plugin for a Blog Platform. - This alone should raise a flag.\n\nI used to love it, when I had a 10 products- shop. - but now, as my product base grew, it becomes really a night mare to take care of. \nHere are a couple of reasons why:\n<ol>\n	<li>Not natively Search engine friendly</li>\n- this comes through a dinosaur URL structure which intervenes with all other taxonomies in the WordPress realm like Posts, pages, and Tags, etc. - A real nice shop should have a fully customizable URL structure, - at best one that follows SEO standards that are about as old as WordPress itself. - They should be like\n<blockquote>domain.tld/product</blockquote> and not have a mandatory category AND Product base.\n	<li>no native fields for e-commerce standards like GTIN, EAN or bas pric calculation (for real, you have to calculate base prices manually in 2020!!!!!)	</li>\n<li>no native product import/export that actually works</li>\n<li>for a csv product import you need to upload a plugin that makes csv uploads possible</li>\n<li>no native customer import/export that actually works</li>\n<li>just paid plugins for everything that is part of every other \"real\" e-commerce solution, making it much more expensive than every other </li>\n<li> Woocommerce Users are no native WP Users</li>\n<li>User Meta Data is bloated - and not even in the same database table as the user itself. - so every Database export wwill be a nightmare, because you have to \"crossreference\" Customer Meta with customer data - (nightmare)</Li>\n\nIf you want a decent shop, you have to calculate at least 600 USD every year into this but still have to fight with priorly mentioned problems. (count in 160 usd for SEO tools that make your product meta descriptions possible</li>\n</ol>\n\n\nAll in all:\n\nWoocommerce is great stuff for beginners, but as soon as you want to get really professional, I would recommend to you to look at Prestashop, Shopware, Magento, Shopify, BigCommerce, XT-Commerce, or Gambio. You will have less trouble AND fewer updates (which are always a guessing game, whether or not your page will break after updating every single plugin) with those.\n\nI would give it 1 Star after my nightmare in migrating a woocommerce shop, but given that it is free to begin with AND it is great for small sites, I give 2 Stars</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.4.9.0.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"sr