 class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Reliable support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dianatoma\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/42d854306200b9c609a70b52f9bd50c6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/42d854306200b9c609a70b52f9bd50c6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dianatoma\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dianatoma</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 13, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I guess the most important thing is that they always answer within a reasonable time frame and they provide all the information available that they can. So thumbs up to everyone!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works great, awesome company!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/derekiaam\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a9807b377b031059eac4c21177fb69d0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a9807b377b031059eac4c21177fb69d0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/derekiaam\" class=\"reviewer-name\">derekiaam</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 12, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We use Events Calendar Pro.  It works great, is quite flexible, and does exactly what we need it to do to run our 2-4 weekly events.  The one time we had an issue I emailed the company and they got back to me with a personalized fix in less than 12 hours.  And the person who helped me was so nice and relatable.  So now they feel like friends. :)  Highly recommended!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Usefull tool to have</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/larisasarduc\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/843b04027b5ca66fc3975b307268ab6f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/843b04027b5ca66fc3975b307268ab6f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/larisasarduc\" class=\"reviewer-name\">larisasarduc</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 10, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple and easy to use, does something very useful for all: keeps us organized.\nI\'m sure there are other plugins to do the same job, but there is no sense in searching for something else.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent event promotion</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oxhums\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/09263553adda8e312583e5542f618f00?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/09263553adda8e312583e5542f618f00?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oxhums\" class=\"reviewer-name\">OxHums</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 9, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have been using Event Calendar for our local group for 5 years now and have always found it a very effective and user friendly event promotion tool.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">calendar view stopped working once it switches to January</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anthonystackowitz\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/34fd81d24a7f9420cc9d921890cdb5ff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/34fd81d24a7f9420cc9d921890cdb5ff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anthonystackowitz\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anthonystackowitz</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 3, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">calendar just stopped working once it switched over to January works fine if i go back in time but what good is that. Also, they never sent me an email to activate -- maybe it\'s that but there is no way to get a hold of them.. \n\nFree stuff that has a pro upgrade I find is not worth it... never seems to work or breaks unless you pay someone...\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very Nice</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mwebs\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bb6ca7539c991bd4bcbd6be3daccdff3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bb6ca7539c991bd4bcbd6be3daccdff3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mwebs\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mwebs</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 24, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Nice Plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No support for pro accounts?</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hellarad\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/35c2b7db95c6ac4c01121fc6a982a875?s=16&#038;d=mo