reviewer-name\">annameis</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 18, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is the best event calendar plug in I have found. I had an issue and they provided timely and great support.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Absolute Garbage</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rdynek\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05fc1121e1bc4a662c567224cdd8f4fd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05fc1121e1bc4a662c567224cdd8f4fd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rdynek\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rdynek</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Does not work. Support ABSOUTELY SUCKS. Do not waste your money</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:70:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/the-events-calendar.5.3.1.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:9:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2234716\";s:7:\"caption\";s:21:\"Month View with hover\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:72:\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/scre