ading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/krek59\" class=\"reviewer-name\">krek59</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 14, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use Yoast for my own sites, but also for my work as a copywriter for clients. Yoast allows me to tweak new copy for keyword optimisation on test pages before I submit my proposal to my clients. Chances are they will use WP with Yoast for their own sites, and they are always pleased to find that my copy scores \'bigly\' on the SEO criteria.\nThank you, Joost, for Yoast.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin for basic SEO</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/irinat\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9a5eb416bad184de1dc41af37391ccf9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9a5eb416bad184de1dc41af37391ccf9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/irinat\" class=\"reviewer-name\">IrinaT</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 14, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We have been using Yoast for years now on all our blogs and it\'s working great for basic SEO and readability checks on our articles and blog posts. You simply set your focus keyword and see how your title, meta tags, and copy reflect your topic. You get a basic analysis of your post, so you can optimize it before publishing. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It breaks the page with forms</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kusatra\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5cb7b87a280cd310e7db98b2a144a6ee?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5cb7b87a280cd310e7db98b2a144a6ee?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kusatra\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ali <small>(kusatra)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 12, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I always had the same issue. And although it is brought up by many other users, each time it is ignored by Yoast. Now finally I give up after waiting for so long time. For God\'s sake there is something in Yoast SEO that break the site with formidable forms. After each update I had to deactivate and re-activate yoast. and after a year now giving up. You should start listening your users instead of ignoring them.</div>\n</div>\n<div 